Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.02,1:48:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,see this is where Newtonian science stops right here
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.05,1:48:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,then quantum mechanics starts to tickle you to go out there
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.05,1:48:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is the world of non-linear dynamics
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.77,1:48:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the world of the linear Newtonian paradigm
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.77,1:48:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is the world of spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.03,1:48:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.57,1:48:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,power is coming from the field
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.57,1:49:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the source of your power
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.80,1:49:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the unenlightened person thinks
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.80,1:49:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if I just strive harder
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.80,1:49:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make more money
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.80,1:49:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work harder longer
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.80,1:49:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,spend more money on advertising
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.14,1:49:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,cut down my employees wages
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.14,1:49:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,push the envelope as hard as I can
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.14,1:49:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that's looking at it from causality
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.68,1:49:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,if I push harder here
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.68,1:49:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win more there
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.68,1:49:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too lazy to do that
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.89,1:49:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.89,1:49:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather be good at winning
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.89,1:49:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what I do
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.89,1:49:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and let them come to me
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.89,1:49:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,why should I push for customers
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.51,1:49:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so context brings you effortlessly
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.51,1:49:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what you cannot achieve with effort
